--- of the same threat direction.
---
--- Higher value = fewer walls, less chance of overlap
--- Lower value = more separate walls, better coverage
---
--- Value is a cosine angle:
--- 0.95 ≈ 18 degrees
--- 0.87 ≈ 30 degrees
------------------------------------------------------

TargetGroupingAngle = 0.95



------------------------------------------------------
