------------------------------------------------------
--- Controls the number and spacing of drones in each wall.
--- Increase rows/columns for a larger shield surface.
--- MAY CAUSE AN ERROR IF THE AMOUNT OF SLOTS (ROWS*COLUMNS) IS INFERIOR TO THE NUMBER OF DRONES
------------------------------------------------------

